This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=2411

A port of the M-x yow feature in Emacs.  Entering the command :Yow earns you a random Zippy The Pinhead quote.

The quotes are stored in the file "yow.lines", which i borrowed from Emacs.

Defining your own quotes is possible by changing yow.lines.  The format is explained in the yow.lines file.
